data.description: Welcome to the beautiful city of Temple Tx, this amazing home is located in the highly sought-after neighborhood of Windmill Farms. Walk into a spacious living area that flows into the separate dining room and kitchen area. Enjoy the beautiful Texas weather with your oversized backyard and oversized patio area. (Shed comes with the home!) Conveniently located next to lake Belton Hs, Take a small drive to Belton Lake for all your fun water activities! Don't miss this opportunity to own such a beautiful home in a great location, schedule your private tour now!
